The repository integrates with external benchmark ecosystems, including
SkillsBench and tau-bench. Those upstream projects, their datasets, and any
checked-out benchmark code remain subject to their own licenses and terms.

Tracked release artifacts in this repository document the SIP-Bench protocol
layer, schemas, runners, and example outputs. Run-local caches, prepared task
copies, and local secret files are excluded from the intended release surface.
